{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/8002","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/8002/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/8002/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/issues/8002/events","html_url":"https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/issues/8002","id":2316800186,"node_id":"I_kwDOAxkop86KF5C6","number":8002,"title":"Replace cstr! macro with C-string literal syntax","user":{"login":"dan-arnold","id":1354164,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzNTQxNjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1354164?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold","html_url":"https://github.com/dan-arnold","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dan-arnold/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":327960157,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwzMjc5NjAxNTc=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/alacritty/alacritty/labels/enhancement","name":"enhancement","color":"84b6eb","default":true,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2024-05-25T07:31:53Z","updated_at":"2025-07-01T14:52:10Z","closed_at":"2025-07-01T14:52:10Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Currently, in the renderer [there is a macro](https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/blob/cacdb5bb3b72bad2c729227537979d95af75978f/alacritty/src/renderer/mod.rs#L36) called `cstr!` which is used to get a pointer to a string literal as a CStr.\r\n\r\nFrom <https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/edition-guide/rust-2021/c-string-literals.html>:\r\n> Starting with Rust 1.77, C-strings can be written using C-string literal syntax with the c or cr prefix.\r\n> ...\r\n> Now, C-strings can be written directly using literal syntax notation, which will generate a value of type [&core::ffi::CStr](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/ffi/struct.CStr.html) which is automatically terminated with a NUL byte.\r\n\r\n\r\nThis is the same behavior as the `cstr!` macro.\r\n\r\nI think we should remove the `cstr!` macro and replace calls to it with `c\"mystring\"` instead. However, this change would require a bump of the rust-version to 1.77.","closed_by":{"login":"kchibisov","id":27620401,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI3NjIwNDAx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/27620401?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov","html_url":"https://github.com/kchibisov","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kchibisov/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/